- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper deals with training deep learning models.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a possible category as the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed method on image datasets.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with deep learning, which is a subfield of AI.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on data structures or algorithms, but rather on the use of low precision posits for DNN training.
